topic.title: N1QL Error Codes
topic.shortdesc: The following table lists all of the N1QL error codes, their error message, and some tips to resolve them.

section.title: 1xx Codes (shell)
section.p:
These errors are related to the shell.
ICode Error Message Description Cause / Suggestion
Connection Errors
100 CONNECTION_REFUSED ___
Connection refused.
101 UNSUPPORTED_PROTOCOL ___ Unsupported protocol scheme.
102 NO_SUCH_HOST ___ No such host.
103 NO_HOST_IN_URL ___ No host in request URL.
104 UNKNOWN_PORT_TCP ___ Unknown port.
105 NO_ROUTE_TO_HOST ___ No route to host.
106 UNREACHABLE_NETWORK ___ Network is unreachable.
107 NO_CONNECTION ___ Not connected to any cluster. Use \\CONNECT command.
108 DRIVER_OPEN ___ Driver open.
109 INVALID_URL ___ Invalid input URL.
Read/Write/Update file errors
116 READ_FILE ___ Error during file read.
117 WRITE_FILE ___ Error during file write.
118 FILE_OPEN ___ Unable to open file.
119 FILE_CLOSE ___ Unable to close file.
Authentication Errors
121 INVALID_PASSWORD ___ Invalid password.
122 INVALID_USERNAME ___ Invalid username.
123 MISSING_CREDENTIAL ___ Username missing in -credentials/-c option.
124 INVALID_CREDENTIAL ___ Invalid format for credentials. Separate username and password by a :.
Command Errors
136 NO_SUCH_COMMAND ___ Command does not exist.
137 NO_SUCH_PARAM ___ Parameter does not exist.
138 TOO_MANY_ARGS ___ Too many input arguments to command.
139 TOO_FEW_ARGS ___ Too few input arguments to command.
140 STACK_EMPTY ___ Stack empty.
141 NO_SUCH_ALIAS ___ Alias does not exist.
142 BATCH_MODE ___ Error when running in batch mode. Incorrect input value
143 STRING_WRITE ___ Cannot write to string buffer.
Generic Errors
170 OPERATION_TIMEOUT ___ Operation timed out. Check query service URL.
171 ROWS_SCAN ___ Error in scanning a row.
172 JSON_MARSHAL ___ Error in marshalling the JSON data.
173 JSON_UNMARSHAL ___ Error in unmarshalling the JSON data.
174 DRIVER_QUERY ___ Error in the query driver.
175 WRITER_OUTPUT ___
Error with I/O Writer.
176 UNBALANCED_PAREN ___ Unbalanced parenthesis in the input.
177 ROWS_CLOSE ___ Error in closing the row.
178 CMD_LINE_ARG ___ Place input argument URL at the end, after input flags.
179 INVALID_INPUT_ARGUMENTS ___ Input Argument format is invalid.
Untracked Errors
199 UNKNOWN_ERROR ___ Unknown error.

section.title: 1xxx Codes (service)
section.p:
These errors are related to the service.
ICode Error Message Description Cause / Suggestion
1050 No ___ value Missing value.
1060 Multiple values for ___ Multiple values for that feature.
1065 Unrecognized parameter in request: ___ Unrecognized parameter in that request.
1070 ___ has to be of type ___ Type mismatch. Another type was expected.
1080 Timeout ___ exceeded Timeout was exceeded.
1100 Invalid JSON in results Invalid JSON in results.
1110 forbidden character (\\ or \") in client_context_id Forbidden character (\ or ") in client_context_id. Remove the \ or " in client_context_id.
1120 Unsupported media type: ___ Unsupported media type.
1130 Request ___ is not a http request Request is not an HTTP request.
1140 Array ___ should be of length 2 Array should be of length 2.
1150 Bad sequence number ___. Expected an unsigned 64-bit integer. Bad sequence number. Use an unsigned 64-bit integer.
1150 Bad UUID ___. Expected a string. Bad UUID. Use a string value.
1160 Failed to decode nil value. Failed to decode nil value.
1170 Unsupported method ___ Unsupported HTTP method.

Bad service port.

section.p:
These codes are related to parsing.
ICode Error Message Description Cause / Suggestion

section.p:
These error are related to the query plan.

4010 ___ term must have a name or alias Term must have a name or alias.
4020 Duplicate ___ alias ___ Duplicate alias.

4030 FROM in correlated subquery must have USE KEYS clause: FROM ___ FROM in correlated subquery must have USE KEYS clause.
4040 No such prepared statement: ___ No such prepared statement.
4050 Unrecognizable prepared statement Unrecognizable prepared statement.
4060 Unable to add name: ___ Unable to add prepared name.
4070 Unable to decode prepared statement Unable to decode prepared statement.
4080 Encoded plan parameter does not match encoded plan of ___ Encoded plan parameter does not match this encoded plan.
4090 Prepared name in encoded plan parameter is not ___ Prepared name in encoded plan parameter is mismatched.
4100 No index available for join term ___ No index available for this JOIN term.
4110 ___ term should not have USE KEYS This should not have USE KEYS.
4210 Expression must be a group key or aggregate: ___ This expression must be a group key or aggregate.
4300 The index ___ already exists. The index already exists.
4310 META() in query with multiple FROM terms requires an argument. META() in query with multiple FROM terms requires an argument.
4320 DESC option in the index keys is not supported by indexer. DESC option in the index keys is not supported by indexer.
4321 Plan error: ___ Plan internal error.

section.title: 5000 & 9999 Codes (errors)
section.p:
These are general errors.
ICode Error Message Description Cause / Suggestion
5000 Internal Error Internal Error.
9999 not_implemented Not yet implemented.
